	<span style="font-size: 12px;">This fun decoration is a great way to get everyone excited and into the Christmas spirit. The block base is not large so it is ideal to put anywhere around the house or even in a child&rsquo;s bedroom so they have a personal reminder. The countdown contains a &lsquo;Sleeps till Christmas&rsquo; double block base and two number cubes. The countdown can start from around a month before christmas until exciting Christmas Eve. The base measures 10cm x 3cm and is 6.5cm tall.</span></p>
